REQURED PACKAGES
For compiling sources and general command line development, you need these
packages. All are installed via apt-get.

  build-essential
  vim
  git
GIT
  libssl-dev
  libcurl4-openssl-dev
  libexpat1-dev
  texlive-full (this takes a few hours...)
  asciidoc
  xmlto
  docbook2x
PYTHON
  libpython3-dev
  python3-setuptools
  python3-psutil
MATPLOTLIB
  libpng12-dev
  libfreetype6-dev
  python3-dateutil
  python3-pyparsing
  python3-cairo-dev *
  libffi-dev *
  python3-tk
  tk-dev
SCIPY
  gfortran
  liblapack-dev
ROOT
  libxpm-dev
OTHERS
  libgtk2.0-dev
